    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/733fda07f0994c3daad09c9e82052c0a.poster.avif?t=1764203776\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/733fda07f0994c3daad09c9e82052c0a.webm?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/733fda07f0994c3daad09c9e82052c0a.mp4?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被传送到邪神的领域，在创造者赐予你不朽之后，踏上拯救家园星球的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找拥有魔力的装备，在旅途中击败成群的怪物。你能消灭邪恶势力，成为真正的猎神者吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>单人 或 合作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/e2b5c5be17843363df0f24839b6061ac.poster.avif?t=1764203776\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/e2b5c5be17843363df0f24839b6061ac.webm?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/e2b5c5be17843363df0f24839b6061ac.mp4?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>独自或合作击败所有敌人，同步你的构筑和策略，分享战利品，让邪神为他们的选择后悔！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>两款游戏合二为一</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/421dad44d49da8f23637ba79a1b75758.poster.avif?t=1764203776\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/421dad44d49da8f23637ba79a1b75758.webm?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/421dad44d49da8f23637ba79a1b75758.mp4?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第一个传送门会带你深入星球内部，寻找并最终击败其神明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在另一个模式中，你将在大型开放地图上战斗，尽可能坚持更久，阻止入侵力量抵达你的世界。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>难度等级 &amp; BOSS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/bb26b77a61639f40f105a1e0fc1724a4.poster.avif?t=1764203776\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/bb26b77a61639f40f105a1e0fc1724a4.webm?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/bb26b77a61639f40f105a1e0fc1724a4.mp4?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击杀巨大的首领！每获得一个首领之魂都会提升难度，并解锁新的敌人、挑战、武器和物品。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>钩子终结技 &amp; 武器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/ad2be5d759e9d8725e135c37276458ad.poster.avif?t=1764203776\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/ad2be5d759e9d8725e135c37276458ad.webm?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/ad2be5d759e9d8725e135c37276458ad.mp4?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>使用你的链钩更快地移动，对低血量敌人执行终结技，并在每次探索中找到拥有独特技能的强力武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找敌人身上的可破坏部位，在战斗中削弱他们。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>宝箱 &amp; 物品</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/ae275ec31560bcf1eb7ed3598e4b69c9.poster.avif?t=1764203776\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/ae275ec31560bcf1eb7ed3598e4b69c9.webm?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/ae275ec31560bcf1eb7ed3598e4b69c9.mp4?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现强大的魔法宝箱，每个都包含不同的升级、增益、物品和武器。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>升级 &amp; 同伴</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/507e89b39234025e7c928d1e6648fb11.poster.avif?t=1764203776\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/507e89b39234025e7c928d1e6648fb11.webm?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1338490/extras/507e89b39234025e7c928d1e6648fb11.mp4?t=1764203776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救会在旅途中帮助你的可爱伙伴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用战斗中收集的水晶永久强化自己！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开发者寄语：我们真心希望你玩得尽兴 💗</p>",
